@node "_introduction" "  INTRODUCTION  "
@prev "Main"

This piece of software is used to make FTP requests to Aminet FTP by mail
servers...

I decided to write AFM a few months ago, because all other software didn't
seem to work, or needed 3/4 libraries that i didn't have...


FEATURES:

        o MUI Interface
        o Internal Rexx support
        o NO Aminet Mailing List subscription necessary
        o Mail Merge (currently only for 2 servers)
        o Multiple Server option
        o "Reply to" option
        o .Readme download option
        o Selectable Aminet folder (in YAM)
        o Size of selected files displayed
        o It works!!! (As far has I can tell)

The software has been tested by a few AFM users and me so I
think there aren't any major bugs.


@endnode

